17:00.399 --> 17:01.742
Youngest!

17:06.839 --> 17:09.410
Can we offer you a ride?

17:12.044 --> 17:15.423
Is there a town close by?
AAA said that there's nothing for miles.

17:16.013 --> 17:17.857
Yeah, we're pretty far out.

17:17.915 --> 17:20.453
