20:39.818 --> 20:41.092
They aren't old, right?

20:41.153 --> 20:44.259
But they act like they're 80,
and from the '50s.

20:44.623 --> 20:47.035
I bet they have the nastiest sex!

20:48.026 --> 20:50.233
Wait. Did you guys hear that?

20:50.629 --> 20:52.302
What are you talking about?

20:52.364 --> 20:55.038
Kim, this totally looks like you!

20:55.300 --> 20:57.746
You're, like, a hot milkmaid.

20:58.870 --> 21:01.510
