Lucas, are you okay?

34:06.757 --> 34:07.963
I gotta call you back.

34:08.025 --> 34:11.130
...keep on moving forward.

34:11.195 --> 34:14.404
Try not to linger
on the things you left behind.

34:14.931 --> 34:17.503
Because you cannot undo
what's been done...

34:18.402 --> 34:20.404
And ain't nobody gonna...

34:35.920 --> 34:38.491
Hello? Hey! Are you okay?

34:39.422 --> 34:40.766
Miss, I...

34:53.871 --> 34:55.110
Hi, hey.

34:55.505 --> 34:57.281
Lucas, are you okay?

34:57.475 --> 34:58.681
Yeah.

34:58.743 --> 35:00.086
