35:35.813 --> 35:40.057
You just hit a woman with your car...
With your car. Was she on foot?

35:40.117 --> 35:44.896
Yes. She's in the road right now,
and she's very badly hurt.

35:44.956 --> 35:46.765
- Okay.
- She's very badly hurt.

35:46.824 --> 35:48.360
