35:48.426 --> 35:49.427
I'm on...

35:51.362 --> 35:53.239
I'm on... I don't know where I am.

35:53.297 --> 35:54.901
You know what,
I'm in the middle of nowhere.

35:54.966 --> 35:56.946
Sir, I'm sorry, sir, you're breaking up.

35:57.001 --> 35:59.538
I said I'm in the middle of nowhere.

36:02.073 --> 36:03.143
