36:40.678 --> 36:41.918
She's...

36:43.381 --> 36:45.657
She's got a head trauma,

36:45.716 --> 36:49.664
and some broken bones,
multiple broken bones, I think.

36:49.720 --> 36:51.256
Okay. Anything else?

36:52.957 --> 36:56.530
She's got a compound fracture of her knee.
I think.

36:56.694 --> 36:58.037
- Is she breathing?
- Yeah.

36:58.329 --> 37:00.832
- Okay. Is she conscious?
- God damn it, Claire.

37:00.898 --> 37:03.071
- All right, sir, you're doing fine. Sir?
- Yeah.

37:03.134 --> 37:05.011
Lucas? Lucas?

37:05.803 --> 37:07.077
How do you know my name?

37:07.138 --> 37:08.708
We have your cell.

37:09.573 --> 37:11.780
- Right. Of course. Yeah.
- You need to trust us, okay?

37:11.842 --> 37:12.912
Okay.

37:12.977 --> 37:15.651
Sir, she's in critical condition
and we can't seem to locate you,

37:15.713 --> 37:17.624
